    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/2de4159704f35d613c4485226c041ec6.avif?t=1728896760\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras_big/2de4159704f35d613c4485226c041ec6.avif?t=1728896760 width=800 height=240 /></span>In Little Repair Shop you will receive requests from customers who will ask you to <strong>repair their beloved consoles</strong>.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After accepting the request, the order will arrive at your desk and the process can begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/816abc6fd4e5912b5ffc08f287e18b5a.poster.avif?t=1728896760\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/816abc6fd4e5912b5ffc08f287e18b5a.webm?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/816abc6fd4e5912b5ffc08f287e18b5a.mp4?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you repair also becomes<strong> part of your collection</strong> and can be <strong>customized </strong>with new <strong>colors</strong>, <strong>patterns </strong>and <strong>stickers</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/c05befc2142ff1d1e1dba6612eee9d44.poster.avif?t=1728896760\" width=638 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/c05befc2142ff1d1e1dba6612eee9d44.webm?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/c05befc2142ff1d1e1dba6612eee9d44.mp4?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a <strong>cozy and relaxing experience</strong>: <strong>take care</strong> of consoles and make them <strong>unique </strong>to create the perfect collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/96c4457924dfcde7dd2da61bd0af79ac.poster.avif?t=1728896760\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/96c4457924dfcde7dd2da61bd0af79ac.webm?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/96c4457924dfcde7dd2da61bd0af79ac.mp4?t=1728896760\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a relaxing, wholesome experience surrounded by pastel colors and relaxing music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Respond to customer requests and help them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Restore old consoles to their former glory!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your consoles with many cute stickers and different color palettes!</p></li></ul>",
